{"tid":1792174,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"勇ONLINE 聖誕大改版 (+15裝備)","createTime":"2019-12-21T12:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T08:15:40.000Z","uid":70687,"like":7,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"db9c1006f7c831d3ea80f7842c4c06de5547ce4c","tid":1792174,"uid":70687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"HI 各位巴絲 <br />\n勇ONLINE就快全新改版推出+15裝備<br />\n呢個時間係入坑好時機<br />\n因為可以誘過打石打貝賺第一桶金<br />\n各勢力都開始招兵買馬<br />\n勇ONLINE官網:<a href=\"http://www.yong-online.com.tw/activities/Yong_act20191217zlao/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yong-online.com.tw%2Factivities%2FYong_act20191217zlao%2Findex.html&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Kf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=7ddff6b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.yong-online.com.tw/activities/Yong_act20191217zlao/index.html</a><br />\n而呢隻GAME最主要都係打架 PVP PVE 亦可以優閒打寶打活動升LV<br />\n大型打架電算公會戰:每星期三，六<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RYe3-iFngs&amp;t=202s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9RYe3-iFngs%26t%3D202s&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Kf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=74501924\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RYe3-iFngs&amp;t=202s</a><br />\n每晚亦都有CDM公會戰:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tDYUloIEmvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtDYUloIEmvA&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Kf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=61882655\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tDYUloIEmvA</a><br />\n<br />\n而公會亦都會不定期舉辦活動 例如聖誕交換禮物 武林大會等等<br />\n而且公會100%全深黃 大家同聲同氣 歡迎加入<br />\ntelegarm:<a href=\"https://t.me/youngonline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyoungonline&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Kf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=87260550\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youngonline</a><br />\n<br />\nBTW.我地唔怕其他敵盟既巴絲加入,歡迎跳槽"},{"pid":"68ac42e2f090b42d1345465a905dabd9b78bc161","tid":1792174,"uid":311583,"l